.SH NAME
customkb \- AI-powered knowledgebase system with semantic search and LLM integration
.
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B customkb
.I command
.RI [ kb_name ]
.RI [ options ]
.br
.B customkb database
.I kb_name
.RI [ files... ]
.RI [ options ]
.br
.B customkb embed
.I kb_name
.RI [ options ]
.br
.B customkb query
.I kb_name
.RI \(dq question \(dq
.RI [ options ]
.br
.B customkb categorize
.I kb_name
.RI [ options ]
.br
.B customkb optimize
.RI [ kb_name ]
.RI [ options ]
.br
.B customkb edit
.I kb_name
.br
.B customkb bm25
.I kb_name
.RB [ \-\-force ]
.br
.B customkb verify\-indexes
.I kb_name
.br
.B customkb convert\-encoding
.I files...
.RI [ options ]
.br
.B customkb version
.RB [ \-\-build ]
.br
.B customkb help
.
.SH DESCRIPTION
.B customkb
transforms documents into AI-powered, searchable knowledgebases using vector
embeddings, FAISS indexing, and LLM integration.
It supports multiple AI providers (OpenAI, Anthropic, Google, xAI, Ollama)
via LiteLLM and delivers contextually relevant answers from your data.
.PP
The system follows a three-stage pipeline:
.IP 1. 4
.B Document Processing
\(em text extraction, language detection, intelligent chunking, and SQLite storage.
.IP 2. 4
.B Embedding Generation
\(em vector embeddings via API or local models, FAISS index creation, two-tier caching.
.IP 3. 4
.B Semantic Query
\(em vector similarity search, optional hybrid BM25, optional reranking, LLM response.
.
.SH COMMANDS
.
.SS database
Process text files into a knowledgebase.
Supports Markdown, HTML, PDF, code files, and plain text.
Auto-detects 27+ languages.
.PP
.B customkb database
.I kb_name
.RI [ files... ]
.RI [ options ]
.TP
.BR \-l ", " \-\-language " " \fILANG\fR
Stopwords language (default: \fBen\fR).
Available: en, fr, de, id, es, etc.
.TP
.B \-\-detect\-language
Auto-detect language per file.
.TP
.BR \-f ", " \-\-force
Force reprocess existing files.
.TP
.BR \-v ", " \-\-verbose
Enable verbose output (default).
.TP
.BR \-q ", " \-\-quiet
Disable verbose output.
.TP
.BR \-d ", " \-\-debug
Enable debug output.
.
.SS embed
Generate vector embeddings for all unembedded chunks in the knowledgebase.
Automatically selects FAISS index type (Flat/IVF/HNSW) based on dataset size.
.PP
.B customkb embed
.I kb_name
.RI [ options ]
.TP
.BR \-r ", " \-\-reset\-database
Reset embedding status flags and regenerate all embeddings.
.TP
.BR \-v " / " \-q " / " \-d
Verbose / quiet / debug output.
.
.SS query
Search a knowledgebase and get AI-powered answers.
.PP
.B customkb query
.I kb_name
.RI \(dq question \(dq
.RI [ options ]
.TP
.BR \-c ", " \-\-context\-only
Return retrieved context without generating an AI response.
.TP
.BR \-m ", " \-\-model " " \fIMODEL\fR
AI model to use for response generation.
Model aliases are resolved via \fBModels.json\fR.
.TP
.BR \-k ", " \-\-top\-k " " \fIN\fR
Number of search results to retrieve (default: 50).
.TP
.BR \-s ", " \-\-context\-scope " " \fIN\fR
Context segments per result.
.TP
.BR \-t ", " \-\-temperature " " \fIFLOAT\fR
Response creativity, 0.0\(en2.0 (default: 0.0).
.TP
.BR \-M ", " \-\-max\-tokens " " \fIN\fR
Maximum response tokens (default: 4000).
.TP
.BR \-f ", " \-\-format " " \fIFORMAT\fR
Output format: \fBxml\fR (default), \fBjson\fR, \fBmarkdown\fR, \fBplain\fR.
.TP
.BR \-p ", " \-\-prompt\-template " " \fITEMPLATE\fR
Response style: \fBdefault\fR, \fBinstructive\fR, \fBscholarly\fR, \fBconcise\fR,
\fBanalytical\fR, \fBconversational\fR, \fBtechnical\fR.
.TP
.BR \-R ", " \-\-role " " \fIROLE\fR
Custom system role for AI.
.TP
.BR \-Q ", " \-\-query_file " " \fIFILE\fR
Read query text from file.
.TP
.B \-\-category " " \fICATEGORY\fR
Filter results by category (exact match).
.TP
.B \-\-categories " " \fICATEGORIES\fR
Filter results by multiple categories (comma-separated).
.TP
.B \-\-context\-files " " \fIFILES...\fR
Additional context files to include in the query.
.TP
.BR \-v " / " \-q " / " \-d
Verbose / quiet / debug output.
.
.SS categorize
Auto-categorize articles in a knowledgebase using AI.
.PP
.B customkb categorize
.I kb_name
.RI [ options ]
.TP
.BR \-S ", " \-\-sample " " \fIN\fR
Process only \fIN\fR sample articles.
.TP
.BR \-f ", " \-\-full
Process all articles.
.TP
.B \-\-fresh
Ignore checkpoint, reprocess all articles.
.TP
.B \-\-import
Import categories to database after processing.
.TP
.B \-\-list
List existing categories and counts.
.TP
.BR \-m ", " \-\-model " " \fIMODEL\fR
AI model for categorization (default: \fBclaude-haiku-4-5\fR).
.TP
.BR \-s ", " \-\-sampling " " \fIT\-M\-B\fR
Chunk sampling config, e.g., \fB5\-10\-5\fR for top-middle-bottom.
.TP
.BR \-M ", " \-\-max\-concurrent " " \fIN\fR
Maximum concurrent API requests (default: 5).
.TP
.BR \-c ", " \-\-confidence\-threshold " " \fIFLOAT\fR
Minimum confidence for category assignment (default: 0.5).
.TP
.BR \-D ", " \-\-no\-dedup
Disable category deduplication.
.TP
.B \-\-dedup\-threshold " " \fIFLOAT\fR
Similarity threshold for deduplication (default: 85.0).
.TP
.B \-\-fixed\-categories
Use fixed number of categories per article.
.TP
.BR \-v " / " \-q " / " \-d
Verbose / quiet / debug output.
.
.SS optimize
Auto-optimize performance settings based on system resources.
When run without a \fIkb_name\fR, shows system-wide recommendations.
.PP
.B customkb optimize
.RI [ kb_name ]
.RI [ options ]
.TP
.BR \-n ", " \-\-dry\-run
Preview changes without applying.
.TP
.BR \-a ", " \-\-analyze
Analyze and show recommendations.
.TP
.BR \-s ", " \-\-show\-tiers
Display all memory tier settings.
.TP
.BR \-m ", " \-\-memory\-gb " " \fIGB\fR
Override detected memory (in GB).
.TP
.BR \-v " / " \-q " / " \-d
Verbose / quiet / debug output.
.
.SS edit
Open the knowledgebase configuration file in \fB$EDITOR\fR.
Falls back to the editor specified by the \fBdefault_editor\fR config setting
(default: \fBjoe\fR).
.PP
.B customkb edit
.I kb_name
.
.SS bm25
Build the BM25 keyword index for hybrid search (vector + keyword matching).
Requires \fBenable_hybrid_search = true\fR in the [ALGORITHMS] config section.
.PP
.B customkb bm25
.I kb_name
.RB [ \-\-force ]
.TP
.B \-\-force
Force rebuild of an existing BM25 index.
.
.SS verify\-indexes
Check database index health and report any issues.
.PP
.B customkb verify\-indexes
.I kb_name
.
.SS convert\-encoding
Convert text files to UTF-8 encoding in-place.
.PP
.B customkb convert\-encoding
.I files...
.RI [ options ]
.TP
.B \-\-no\-backup
Do not create backups of original files (backups are on by default).
.TP
.B \-\-dry\-run
Preview changes without converting files.
.TP
.BR \-r ", " \-\-recursive
Process directories recursively.
.TP
.BR \-v " / " \-q " / " \-d
Verbose / quiet / debug output.
.
.SS version
Show version information.
.TP
.B \-\-build
Include build number in output.
.
.SS help
Display usage information and exit.
.
.SH KB NAME RESOLUTION
The \fIkb_name\fR argument is flexible.
All of these resolve to the same knowledgebase:
.PP
.nf
customkb query myproject "test"
customkb query myproject.cfg "test"
customkb query $VECTORDBS/myproject "test"
customkb query $VECTORDBS/myproject/myproject.cfg "test"
.fi
.
.SH CONFIGURATION
CustomKB uses INI-style configuration files stored in
\fB$VECTORDBS/\fIkb_name\fB/\fIkb_name\fB.cfg\fR.
.PP
Configuration hierarchy (highest to lowest priority):
.IP 1. 4
Environment variables (uppercased field names, e.g., \fBQUERY_MODEL\fR)
.IP 2. 4
Values in the \fB.cfg\fR file
.IP 3. 4
Built-in defaults
.
.SS [DEFAULT] Section
.TS
l l l.
Parameter	Default	Description
_
vector_model	text-embedding-3-small	Embedding model
vector_dimensions	1536	Embedding dimensions (auto-updated)
db_min_tokens	100	Minimum chunk size in tokens
db_max_tokens	200	Maximum chunk size in tokens
query_model	claude-sonnet-4-6	LLM for query responses
query_top_k	50	Chunks to retrieve
query_temperature	0.0	Response creativity (0.0\(en2.0)
query_max_tokens	4000	Maximum response tokens
reference_format	xml	Output format (xml/json/markdown/plain)
query_prompt_template	default	Response style template
.TE
.
.SS [ALGORITHMS] Section
.TS
l l l.
Parameter	Default	Description
_
similarity_threshold	0.6	Minimum similarity score (0\(en1)
enable_hybrid_search	false	Combine vector + BM25 search
bm25_weight	0.3	BM25 weight in hybrid mode
enable_reranking	true	Cross-encoder reranking
reranking_model	cross-encoder/ms-marco-MiniLM-L-6-v2	Reranking model
reranking_top_k	20	Results to rerank
.TE
.
.SS [PERFORMANCE] Section
.TS
l l l.
Parameter	Default	Description
_
embedding_batch_size	100	Embeddings per batch
checkpoint_interval	10	Save progress every N batches
cache_thread_pool_size	4	Parallel cache threads
memory_cache_size	10000	LRU cache entries
.TE
.
.SS [API] Section
.TS
l l l.
Parameter	Default	Description
_
api_call_delay_seconds	0.05	Seconds between API calls
api_max_concurrency	8	Maximum parallel API requests
api_max_retries	20	Maximum retry attempts
.TE
.
.SH FILES
.TP
.B $VECTORDBS/\fIkb_name\fB/\fIkb_name\fB.cfg
Knowledgebase configuration file (INI format).
.TP
.B $VECTORDBS/\fIkb_name\fB/\fIkb_name\fB.db
SQLite database containing document chunks, metadata, and categories.
.TP
.B $VECTORDBS/\fIkb_name\fB/\fIkb_name\fB.faiss
FAISS vector index (auto-selected type: Flat, IVF, or HNSW).
.TP
.B $VECTORDBS/\fIkb_name\fB/\fIkb_name\fB.bm25
BM25 keyword index (optional, for hybrid search).
.TP
.B $VECTORDBS/\fIkb_name\fB/logs/
KB-specific log files.
.TP
.B Models.json
Model registry with aliases, providers, and capabilities.
.TP
.B example.cfg
Full example configuration with all available options documented.
.
.SH ENVIRONMENT
.TP
.B VECTORDBS
Knowledgebase base directory (default: \fB/var/lib/vectordbs\fR).
.TP
.B OPENAI_API_KEY
OpenAI API key (for GPT models and text-embedding models).
.TP
.B ANTHROPIC_API_KEY
Anthropic API key (for Claude models).
.TP
.B GOOGLE_API_KEY
Google API key (for Gemini models and gemini-embedding).
.TP
.B XAI_API_KEY
xAI API key (for Grok models).
.TP
.B NLTK_DATA
NLTK data directory location.
.TP
.B EDITOR
Preferred editor for \fBcustomkb edit\fR.
Falls back to the \fBdefault_editor\fR config value, then \fBjoe\fR.
.TP
.B CUDA_VISIBLE_DEVICES
GPU device selection (set by the customkb wrapper script).
.
.SH EXIT STATUS
.TP
.B 0
Success (including help and version output).
.TP
.B 1
Error (unknown command, missing knowledgebase, processing failure, or user interrupt).
.TP
.B 2
Unexpected internal error.
.
.SH EXAMPLES
Create a knowledgebase from Markdown files:
.PP
.nf
mkdir -p "$VECTORDBS/myproject"
cat > "$VECTORDBS/myproject/myproject.cfg" << 'EOF'
[DEFAULT]
vector_model = text-embedding-3-small
query_model = claude-sonnet-4-6
db_min_tokens = 200
db_max_tokens = 400
EOF

customkb database myproject docs/*.md
customkb embed myproject
customkb query myproject "What are the main features?"
.fi
.PP
Query with specific model and format:
.PP
.nf
customkb query myproject "explain the architecture" \\
  --model gpt-4o-mini --format json --prompt-template technical
.fi
.PP
Context-only retrieval (no LLM response):
.PP
.nf
customkb query myproject "search terms" --context-only
.fi
.PP
Enable and build hybrid search:
.PP
.nf
# Set enable_hybrid_search = true in [ALGORITHMS] section
customkb edit myproject
customkb bm25 myproject
customkb query myproject "keyword-heavy search"
.fi
.PP
Auto-optimize for system resources:
.PP
.nf
customkb optimize myproject
customkb optimize --analyze
customkb optimize myproject --dry-run
.fi
.PP
Categorize documents using AI:
.PP
.nf
customkb categorize myproject --sample 10
customkb categorize myproject --full --import
customkb categorize myproject --list
.fi
.
