.SH MEMORY TIERS
CustomKB auto-configures based on available system memory:
.TS
l l l l l.
Memory	Tier	Batch Size	Cache Size	Hybrid Search
_
<16GB	Low	50	5,000	Disabled
16\(en64GB	Medium	100	10,000	Available
64\(en128GB	High	200	20,000	Enabled
>128GB	Very High	300	50,000	Enabled
.TE
.
.SH SECURITY
.IP \(bu 3
Safe serialization: JSON-only format (zero pickle).
.IP \(bu 3
SQL injection prevention: parameterized queries throughout.
.IP \(bu 3
Path traversal protection: all file paths validated.
.IP \(bu 3
API key security: environment variable storage, never logged.
.IP \(bu 3
Atomic database operations with rollback support.
.
